      <title>卡特彼勒因机械制造商下调全年业绩预期而下滑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/caterpillar-misses-estimates-on-weakening-demand-in-construction</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于全球建筑活动放缓，标志性黄色推土机制造商卡特彼勒公司 (Caterpillar Inc.) 下调了销售预期，其股价出现六个月来最大跌幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/caterpillar-misses-estimates-on-weakening-demand-in-construction</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 30 Oct 2024 10:32:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
